<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Selected Work | Chris Richel Ong</title>

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #111111;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
      }

      header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 24px 60px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 28px;
        flex: 1;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px 24px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 64px;
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p.subtitle {
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #444;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      /* CASE STUDY LAYOUT */
      .case {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
        align-items: start;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .case {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      .thumb {
        width: 100%;
        height: 260px;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: top;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .thumb:hover {
        transform: scale(1.03);
      }

      .text p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 10px 0 0 18px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      /* LIGHTBOX */
      #lightbox {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
        z-index: 9999;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      #lightbox img {
        max-width: 95vw;
        max-height: 85vh;
        object-fit: contain;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      /* VIDEO GRID */
      .video-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
      }

      .video-thumb {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        display: block;
        background: #000;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .video-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      /* MOBILE */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        header {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 18px;
          padding: 20px 24px;
          text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 16px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 42px;
        }

        h2 {
          font-size: 30px;
        }

        main {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .thumb {
          height: 220px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header>
      <div style="font-size:20px; font-weight:600;">
        Chris Richel Ong
      </div>

      <nav>
        <a href="/" style="text-decoration:none; color:#111;">Home</a>
        <a href="/work" style="text-decoration:none; color:#16a34a; font-weight:600;">Work</a>
        <a href="/about" style="text-decoration:none; color:#111;">About</a>
      </nav>

      <a href="mailto:chrisrichelong@gmail.com"
         style="background:#16a34a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:999px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">
        Email an inquiry
      </a>
    </header>

    <main>

      <h1>Selected Work</h1>

      <p class="subtitle">
        Below are examples of improvements made to real business communication and the results that followed, including video testimonials from clients.
      </p>

      <!-- WEBSITE -->
      <h2>Websites</h2>

      <div class="case">

        <div style="position:relative;">
          <img class="thumb"
               src="/work/case-01-web-01.png"
               onclick="openLightbox(this.src)" />

          <div style="
            position:absolute;
            bottom:10px;
            left:10px;
            background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            color:white;
            font-size:12px;
            padding:6px 10px;
            border-radius:999px;
            pointer-events:none;
          ">
            Click to view full page
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text">
          <p>
          This project involved improving how an online product was presented so that customers could understand it faster and make decisions with more confidence.
There was a strong improvement after adding these elements:
          </p>

          <p><b>What was improved:</b></p>

          <ul>
            <li>Trust signals as proof that the business is legitimate (testimonials, “legit check” section, ecommerce proof)</li>
            <li>Made the product easier to understand and added a strong guarantee</li>
            <li>Reorganized content and sections so it flows better (problem, what people wanted, examples/case study)</li>
            <li>Improved check-out experience (added payment details and sidebar trust elements)</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top:12px;">
            <b>Result:</b> The page improved from <strong>an average of 17% to above 30%</strong> after improving clarity, trust and presentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EMAILS -->
      <h2>Emails</h2>

      <div class="case">
        <img class="thumb"
             src="/work/case-01-email-01.png"
             onclick="openLightbox(this.src)" />

        <div class="text">
          <p>
            This project focused on nurturing potential customers after they joined a Facebook group and gave their email. A 7-day sequence was written to nurture them and demonstrate the benefits of the product
          </p>

          <p><b>The sequence was written using:</b></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Storytelling to explain the experience of the product</li>
            <li>Clear focus on common problems customers were facing</li>
            <li>Language customers actually used to describe their situation</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top:12px;">
            <b>Result:</b> The email sequence achieved <strong>65.44% open rate and 11.48% click rate</strong>, showing strong engagement and interest from potential customers during the decision process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- VIDEO TESTIMONIALS -->
      <h2>Video Testimonials</h2>

      <div class="video-grid">

        <div>
          <iframe class="video-thumb" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7UX8cpjlifY" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;margin-top:10px;">
            "I've hired other copywriters before, but no one has nailed it like Chris did! I'm so pleased with the results." - Stacy Brookman, Leadership Coach
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <iframe class="video-thumb" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q1_6nMi4yLI" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;margin-top:10px;">
            "...to any other company out there that wants content, copy, press releases or whatever else, she's a good author, she knows how to write well, she knows how to optimize well for SEO, I highly recommend her..." - Patrick Murray, Founder of On Air Parking
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <iframe class="video-thumb" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JT-sKUanmO8" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;margin-top:10px;">
            "...something you really need to know about Chris, Chris really cares about your success, I can say that 100% without a doubt!" - Jeff Lambert, Author, Race Sponsorships
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <iframe class="video-thumb" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lQv8ypnuSek" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:#555;margin-top:10px;">
            "...she brings something unique to the table, so I'm constantly thrilled with the results I got..." - Willy Lin, WAH Academy
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </main>

    <!-- LIGHTBOX -->
    <div id="lightbox" onclick="closeLightbox()">
      <img id="lightbox-img" />
    </div>

    <script>
      function openLightbox(src) {
        document.getElementById("lightbox").style.display = "flex";
        document.getElementById("lightbox-img").src = src;
        document.body.style.overflow = "hidden";
      }

      function closeLightbox() {
        document.getElementById("lightbox").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("lightbox-img").src = "";
        document.body.style.overflow = "auto";
      }
    </script>

  </body>
</html>